      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission to a variable M Differential Lock. The chassis has been enhanced with essential subframe reinforcement plates to address common floor pan fatigue, and the suspension maintains its original geometry with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. The valvetrain has been recently shimmed to factory specifications, and the rod bearings have been addressed as preventative maintenance. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with a well-enjoyed performance vehicle, the mechanical vitals remain robust, offering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline and near-perfect 50/50 weight distribution.",
