      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW X5 xDrive35i in Alpine White. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and remains in impressive mechanical and cosmetic shape. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish with only minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with standard highway use, and the alloy wheels are free of major curb rash. Inside, the Mocha Dakota leather interior is supple and free of tears, stains, or smoke odors; the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and premium Harman Kardon sound system all function perfectly. Recent comprehensive service includes a fresh synthetic oil change, new cabin air filters, and a multi-point inspection confirming the engine and transmission are performing smoothly. The Continental All-Season tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. This car comes with two keys, the original owner's manual, and a clean title in hand. It is a turnkey luxury SUV that balances performance with everyday utility.",
